<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Au Phil des Pages</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Au Phil des Pages - Clarté, simplicité, sérénité." />
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen text-slate-900 relative overflow-x-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-100 via-yellow-100 to-purple-100">

  <header class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur shadow-sm">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="text-2xl font-black text-purple-700">Au Phil des Pages</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-slate-600">Clarté • Simplicité • Sérénité</div>
      </div>
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/33766179444?text=Bonjour%20Au%20Phil%20des%20Pages%2C%20je%20souhaite%20vous%20envoyer%20un%20document."
        class="rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-green-500 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg"
      >
        WhatsApp direct
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16">
    <section class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
      <div>
        <div class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 shadow">
          🤹 On simplifie la vie
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-black leading-tight">
          Marre des papiers ? 😵<br />
          On va les dompter ensemble 🐉
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-700">
          Ici, les documents compliqués deviennent compréhensibles.
          Moins de stress, plus de clarté… et un peu de bonne humeur en bonus 😄
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a
            href="#prestations"
            class="rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-emerald-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow"
          >
            Voir les prestations
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://paypal.me/REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_LINK"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            class="rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold shadow"
          >
            Payer en ligne
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-[2rem] bg-white p-6 shadow-2xl">
        <img
          src="https://i.postimg.cc/52Knvcwy/Chat-GPT-Image-22-avr-2026-18-50-53.png"
          alt="Illustration"
          class="w-full rounded-[1.5rem] object-cover shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="prestations" class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-8">Les prestations 🎯</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-400 to-red-400 p-6 text-white shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-3xl">🧩</div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-black">Décryptage express</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-white/90 leading-7">
            Un document vous donne envie de lever les yeux au ciel ? Je le traduis en langage clair, simple et humain.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-orange-400 p-6 text-white shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-3xl">✍️</div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-black">Réponse bien ficelée</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-white/90 leading-7">
            Mail, courrier, réponse administrative : on range les idées, on pose les bons mots et on respire.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-indigo-400 p-6 text-white shadow-lg">
          <div class="text-3xl">📚</div>
          <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-black">Synthèse anti-galère</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-white/90 leading-7">
            Contrat d’assurance, devis, document immobilier ou courrier complexe : l’essentiel, sans noyade en eau bureaucratique.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="tarifs" class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-8">Les tarifs 💰</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow">
          <h3 class="font-black text-xl">Décryptage express</h3>
          <p class="text-2xl font-black mt-2">Dès 20 €</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow">
          <h3 class="font-black text-xl">Réponse bien ficelée</h3>
          <p class="text-2xl font-black mt-2">Dès 40 €</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow">
          <h3 class="font-black text-xl">Mission anti-pagaille</h3>
          <p class="text-2xl font-black mt-2">Sur devis</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="mt-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4">Contact 📞</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-4">Un document te fait soupirer ? Envoie-le 😄</p>
      <div class="text-2xl font-black">07 66 17 94 44</div>
      <div class="mt-4 text-slate-700">Email : auphildespages@gmail.com</div>
      <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/33766179444?text=Bonjour%20Au%20Phil%20des%20Pages%2C%20je%20souhaite%20vous%20envoyer%20un%20document."
          class="rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-green-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg"
        >
          WhatsApp direct
        </a>
        <a
          href="mailto:auphildespages@gmail.com"
          class="rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 shadow"
        >
          Envoyer un email
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
